350
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:53,600
I hear that there's a certain flower in the northern lands called the "Hurricane Lily."

351
00:28:53,600 --> 00:28:55,460
When the flower blooms, it is very pretty.

352
00:28:55,460 --> 00:28:57,700
