(T/N: His name means "little jujube")

405
00:33:49,950 --> 00:33:51,820
Let me remind you then.

406
00:33:51,820 --> 00:33:54,400
You used to be dark and small.

407
00:33:54,400 --> 00:33:56,230
You were as skinny as a dried jujube.

408
00:33:56,230 --> 00:33:57,690
